TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {9600=So, your task is to vote for your favorite out of these two beautiful and healthy, and of course vegetarian, bentos. Difficult, I know! The winner will get a $50 ‘shopping spree’ at From Japan With Love., 7650=We are down the the finals of the May Vegetarian Bento Contest!
